# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code (claude.ai/code) when working with code in this repository.

## Project Overview

MentalBreak is a custom EverQuest server built on EQEmu (EverQuest Emulator) with a **3-class multiclassing system**. Players can combine up to 3 classes, accessing spellbooks, abilities, and skills from all joined classes.

## Repository Layout

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `peqsourcecode-main/` | EQEmu C++20 server source (zone, world, login, common libs) |
| `eq-classless-dll-main/` | Client-side DLL injection (DirectInput hooks, UI modifications) |
| `eqemu server/eqemu/quests/` | Perl/Lua quest scripts (200+ zone directories) |
